revision.text: * The inexperienced may want to check out the "How to help" section on the "community portal" article linked on the sidebar. * Remember this page is the most public face of the wiki - test edits are best done on a separate page. * Sections within "<! --" and "-- >" markers (without the spaces) - like this entire section - are hidden comments, and can be separated by several lines. Be sure not to break them.
